## City Gameplay Update - New String Entries
## Add these entries to city/city.stf

# Expulsion System
expulsion_warning	You have been ordered to leave %TU! You have %DI seconds to vacate the city or militia may attack you!
now_attackable_by_militia	The grace period has expired. City militia may now attack you until you leave city limits.
left_city_expulsion_cleared	You have left the city. Expulsion status cleared.
cannot_enter_building_tef	You cannot enter buildings while under city expulsion combat status.
cannot_use_terminal_tef	You cannot use terminals while under city expulsion combat status.
tef_applied_restrictions	You are now in combat with city militia. Building entry and terminal access are restricted.
not_mayor_or_militia	Only the mayor or militia can expel players from the city.
target_not_in_city	Target is not currently within city limits.
expulsion_initiated	Expulsion order has been issued. Target has 120 seconds to leave.
tef_expired	City combat status has expired. Normal access restored.

# Judge Election System
judge_election_started	A city judge election has begun! Citizens may register as candidates and vote over the next 3 days.
judge_election_complete	Judge election has concluded. New judges have been elected.
registered_as_judge_candidate	You have registered as a candidate for city judge.
cannot_run_under_eviction	You cannot run for judge while under eviction proceedings.
already_voted	You have already cast your vote in this election.
vote_recorded	Your vote has been recorded.
no_election_active	There is no active judge election at this time.
already_registered_candidate	You are already registered as a candidate.
invalid_candidate	That is not a valid candidate.
no_candidates	There are no candidates registered for this election.
election_already_active	A judge election is already in progress.
judge_election_started_msg	Judge election started for your city.

# Eviction System
eviction_initiated	Eviction proceedings have been initiated.
eviction_warning_mail_subject	City Eviction Notice
eviction_warning_mail_body	You have been given notice of eviction from %TU. Reason: %TO. You have 7 days to leave the city or file an appeal.
eviction_appeal_filed	Your appeal has been filed and will be reviewed by a city judge.
eviction_appeal_pending	You already have an appeal pending.
eviction_upheld	The judge has upheld your eviction. You are no longer a citizen of this city.
eviction_reversed	The judge has reversed your eviction. You may remain a citizen.
eviction_complete	Your eviction grace period has expired. You are no longer a citizen.
no_eviction_pending	You do not have any eviction pending.
appeal_already_filed	You have already filed an appeal.
eviction_started	Eviction proceedings have been started.

# Extended Taxes
landing_tax_paid	The Imperial Docking Authority of %TU has collected %DI credits in landing fees.
landing_tax_insufficient	You cannot afford the %DI credit landing fee for %TU. You only have %DI credits. Your ship has been redirected outside city limits.
crafting_tax_paid	You have paid %DI credits in crafting tax to %TU.
structure_placement_fee_paid	You have paid %DI credits in structure placement fee to %TU.
set_crafting_tax	Set Crafting Tax
set_vendor_license	Set Vendor License Fee
set_structure_fee	Set Structure Placement Fee
set_landing_tax	Set Starship Landing Tax
extended_taxes	Extended Taxes
tax_updated	Tax has been updated.
invalid_number	Please enter a valid number.

