# Terrain Management
terrain_management	Terrain Management
paint_terrain_radius	Paint Terrain (Radius)
paint_terrain_road	Paint Terrain (Road)
bulldoze_city	Bulldoze City
view_terrain_regions	View Terrain Regions
remove_terrain_region	Remove Terrain Region
terrain_rank_too_low	Your city rank is too low to use this feature.
bulldoze_rank_too_low	Your city must be Rank 3 or higher to bulldoze terrain.
city_already_bulldozed	This city has already been bulldozed.
radius_out_of_range	Radius must be between 5 and your maximum allowed value.
width_out_of_range	Road width must be between 2 and 10 meters.
stand_at_paint_location	Stand at the location where you want to paint terrain.
say_painthere_when_ready	Say '/painthere' when you are ready.
walk_to_road_start	Walk to where you want the road to start.
say_painthere_for_first_marker	Say '/painthere' to set the first marker.
first_marker_set	First road marker set.
walk_to_second_marker	Now walk to where you want the road to end and say '/painthere'.
paint_outside_city	The paint area extends outside city limits.
terrain_painted_radius	Terrain has been painted successfully.
terrain_painted_road	Road terrain has been painted successfully.
city_bulldozed	City terrain has been flattened successfully.
no_terrain_regions	This city has no terrain regions defined.
terrain_region_removed	Terrain region has been removed.
terrain_invalid_params	Invalid terrain command parameters.
terrain_invalid_city	Invalid city specified.
terrain_invalid_type	Invalid terrain modification type.
terrain_region_not_found	Terrain region not found.
click_to_paint_radius	Stand at the center of where you want to paint, then say '/painthere'.
radius_exceeds_limit	Radius exceeds the maximum allowed for your city rank.
terrain_modify	Terrain modification message.




